The Fighters Who Took Over a Retail Store to Defend Kyiv

By Yousur Al-Hlou, Masha Froliak, Brent McDonald, Mark Boyer and Benjamin Foley•March 29, 2022

As Russia pledges to scale back operations in Kyiv, soldiers from the 112th Brigade of Ukraine’s Territorial Defense Forces are still preparing for the worst. Our cameras went inside their makeshift base.
